EFL Mkhi taking St Etienne 0 Manchester United 1 (agg 0-4): Henrikh Mkhitaryan seals easy passage through but his goal could come at a costly price 
Armenian limped off 10 minutes after his goal and is now a doubt for the EFL Cup final against Southampton on Sunday By Mike McGrath & Richard Forrester 22nd February 2017, 6:50 pm
